 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Develop a C#/WPF app that manages user roles and permissions securely."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Integrate a robust WPF security library, design a secure UserRoleManagementService with encryption, and develop a user-friendly UI for role management\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research existing WPF security libraries\",\"description\":\"Investigate and document any existing WPF libraries for handling user roles and permissions, focusing on their strengths, weaknesses, and compatibility with .NET Core.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Design the User Role Management Service\",\"description\":\"Create a C# service (e.g., Services/UserRoleManagementService.cs) that handles user roles and permissions. The service should include methods for adding, removing, and updating user roles, as well as checking permissions.\"},{\"role\":\"UIDEVELOPER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Design the User Role Management UI\",\"description\":\"Develop a WPF window or dialog (e.g., Views/UserRoleManagementView.xaml) that allows administrators to manage user roles and view permissions. The interface should be intuitive and user-friendly.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify User Role Management functionality\",\"description\":\"Test the UserRoleManagementService to ensure it correctly handles user roles and permissions according to business requirements. Test scenarios should include adding new roles, removing existing ones, updating permissions, and verifying access controls.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T00:36:40", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 39. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
