 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Integrate a barcode scanning device with the C#/WPF application."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Integrate a barcode scanning library into the C#/WPF application, design a user interface for initiating scans, and test the functionality using a research-driven approach\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research Barcode Scanning APIs\",\"description\":\"Explore available barcode scanning libraries compatible with C# and WPF, such as ZXing.Net or ScanBarcode.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Integrate Barcode Scanner Library\",\"description\":\"Integrate the chosen barcode scanning library into the WPF application. Create a new class, e.g., `BarcodeScannerService.cs`, to handle the scanning logic.\"},{\"role\":\"UIDEVELOPER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Design Barcode Scanning UI\",\"description\":\"Design and implement the user interface for initiating barcode scans, typically a button or a dedicated area in the main window. Implement `BarcodeScannerWindow.xaml` and related XAML files.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify Barcode Scanning Functionality\",\"description\":\"Test the barcode scanning functionality to ensure it accurately detects and reads barcodes. Verify that the system handles different types of barcodes and edge cases, such as scanning in low light or with poor contrast.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T01:00:21", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 71. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
