 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Develop a feature in WPF app for uploading files to cloud storage."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Integrate Azure Storage SDK, design drag-and-drop UI, implement asynchronous file uploads, and test with various file types\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research existing libraries for cloud storage integration\",\"description\":\"Explore and document available .NET libraries that support integration with various cloud storage services (e.g., Azure Blob Storage, AWS S3). Identify the most suitable library based on features, ease of use, and community support.\"},{\"role\":\"UIDEVELOPER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Design file upload UI\",\"description\":\"Create a user-friendly interface for file selection and uploading. Design should include drag-and-drop functionality, progress indicators, and error messages. Implement this in MainWindow.xaml.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Implement file upload logic\",\"description\":\"Develop the backend code to handle file uploads using the chosen cloud storage library. Write the necessary services and methods in Services/FileUploadService.cs. Ensure proper error handling and logging.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify file upload functionality\",\"description\":\"Test the file upload feature with various file types and sizes to ensure it works correctly across different scenarios. Confirm that errors are handled gracefully and that progress indicators update accurately.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T01:43:57", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 134. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
