 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Develop an API integration for third-party payment gateways in our web application."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Identify supported gateways, create interface, implement specific solutions, and test integration\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Identify Supported Payment Gateways\",\"description\":\"Research and list all third-party payment gateways that our web application needs to support.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Create Payment Gateway Interface\",\"description\":\"Design and implement an interface in C# (e.g., IPaymentGateway.cs) that defines the methods for each gateway (e.g., Authorize, Capture, Refund).\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Implement Specific Payment Gateways\",\"description\":\"Develop classes that implement the IPaymentGateway interface for each supported payment gateway (e.g., PayPalService.cs, StripeService.cs).\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Test Payment Gateway Integration\",\"description\":\"Verify that all payment gateways can be successfully integrated and tested with various transaction scenarios.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T01:48:40", "notes": "Normalized from ha