 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Integrate with an existing API to fetch stock market data every hour."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Identify API, create StockService class, schedule hourly data fetching, and verify\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Identify Appropriate API\",\"description\":\"Research and select a free or paid stock market data API that provides the necessary historical and current stock data.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Create StockService Class\",\"description\":\"Develop a C# class named `StockService` in the file `Services/StockService.cs`. This class should include methods to fetch and parse stock data from the selected API.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Schedule Data Fetching\",\"description\":\"Implement a scheduled task using a library like Hangfire or Task Scheduler in the `Services/DataSchedulerService.cs` file. This service should call the `StockService` methods every hour to fetch and store stock data.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify Data Fetching\",\"description\":\"Test that the `StockService` class correctly fetches and parses stock data from the API. Ensure that the scheduled task is running and fetching data as expected.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T02:14:33", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 192. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
