 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Develop a reporting tool that generates dashboards from various data sources."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Identify data sources, design model, build interface, verify integration\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Identify Data Sources and Requirements\",\"description\":\"Gather details about the various data sources the tool needs to support and the specific requirements for dashboard features.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Design and Implement Data Model\",\"description\":\"Create a robust data model that can handle data from different sources. Develop classes like DataModel.cs, DataSourceAdapter.cs, etc.\"},{\"role\":\"UIDEVELOPER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Build Dashboard Interface\",\"description\":\"Design and implement the user interface for the dashboard, including widgets, charts, and layout components. Create files such as DashboardView.xaml, ChartWidget.xaml, etc.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify Data Integration and Display\",\"description\":\"Test that data is correctly integrated from various sources and displayed accurately on the dashboard. Ensure all widgets and charts function as expected.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "orig