 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: 39. Develop a feature to export inventory data as CSV files."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Develop InventoryService.cs, design InventoryExportDialog.xaml, and implement CSV export functionality in the service\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Create InventoryService.cs\",\"description\":\"Implement the InventoryService class with a method ExportToCSV that takes an inventory list and returns a CSV formatted string.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify CSV Export Functionality\",\"description\":\"Test the ExportToCSV method with various inventory data to ensure it generates correct CSV output.\"},{\"role\":\"UIDEVELOPER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Design InventoryExportDialog.xaml\",\"description\":\"Create a dialog window for users to select the inventory data they want to export and specify the file path.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-12T22:58:49", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 224. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
