 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Optimize data transfer between devices over a network."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Identify optimal network protocols, implement data compression, and validate transfer speed\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Identify Network Protocols\",\"description\":\"Research and document common network protocols used for data transfer, such as TCP/IP, HTTP/HTTPS, and WebSockets.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Implement Compression\",\"description\":\"Create a utility class (e.g., CompressionUtils.cs) that implements data compression algorithms like Gzip or Brotli to reduce the size of data being transferred over the network.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Validate Data Transfer Speed\",\"description\":\"Design and execute tests to measure the impact of data compression on transfer speeds between devices. Use tools like Wireshark for capturing network traffic and analyzing performance.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T02:53:29", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 284. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
