 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Refactor legacy C# classes to utilize dependency injection."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Refactor legacy C# classes by researching best practices, applying constructor-based DI in UserService.cs, injecting and using UserService in UserController.cs, and verifying dependencies in tests\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research best practices for dependency injection in C#\",\"description\":\"Gather information on modern patterns and tools for implementing dependency injection in C#, including frameworks like Microsoft.Extensions.DependencyInjection.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Refactor UserService.cs to use constructor-based dependency injection\",\"description\":\"Update the UserService class to accept dependencies via its constructor instead of using static methods or property setters.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Refactor UserController.cs to inject and use UserService\",\"description\":\"Modify the UserController class to receive an instance of UserService through dependency injection and update it accordingly.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify all dependencies are correctly injected in tests\",\"description\":\"Ensure that all unit tests for classes that use dependency injection pass after refactoring, confirming that the correct objects are being injected.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T03:21:56", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 332. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
