 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: 27. Write integration tests for the API integration with the latest weather API."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Write unit tests to verify endpoints, error handling, and response data structure for the latest weather API integration\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify Weather API Integration Endpoints\",\"description\":\"Test all endpoints in the API to ensure they correctly fetch and return weather data from the latest weather API.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Check Error Handling for Invalid Requests\",\"description\":\"Test error handling when making requests with invalid parameters or authentication tokens.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Validate Data Structure of API Responses\",\"description\":\"Verify that the data structure returned by the API matches the expected format and contains all necessary fields.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T04:04:45", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 414. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
