 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: 57. Design and implement a logging system for all C#/WPF applications to provide detailed insights into application performance."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Investigate, design, implement, and test a custom C#/WPF logging system using an existing framework as a base\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Investigate existing logging frameworks\",\"description\":\"Research popular logging frameworks such as NLog, log4net, and Serilog for their compatibility with C#/WPF applications and performance features.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Create a custom logger service\",\"description\":\"Develop a custom logging service (e.g., Services/CustomLoggerService.cs) that integrates the chosen framework and implements a consistent logging interface for all C#/WPF applications.\"},{\"role\":\"UIDEVELOPER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Design a logging configuration UI\",\"description\":\"Create a user-friendly interface (e.g., in MainWindow.xaml or SettingsWindow.xaml) that allows administrators to configure logging levels, output destinations, and format settings.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify logging functionality across applications\",\"description\":\"Test the logging system across various C#/WPF applications to ensure it captures detailed insights into application performance without impacting application speed or reliability.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T04:04:56", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 415. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
