 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: 37. Refactor the PowerShell script to use advanced performance optimization techniques."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Identify bottlenecks, optimize script using advanced techniques, verify improvement\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Identify Performance Bottlenecks\",\"description\":\"Analyze the existing PowerShell script to identify areas where performance can be optimized.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Optimize Script with Advanced Techniques\",\"description\":\"Refactor the identified bottlenecks using advanced performance optimization techniques such as parallel processing, caching, and efficient data structures. Modify the script in Services/ScriptOptimizer.ps1.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify Performance Improvement\",\"description\":\"Test the optimized script to ensure that it performs better than the original version.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T04:06:44", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 420. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
