 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Integrate a new API into our backend services."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Conduct research on the API documentation, create an API client in code, and verify integration through testing\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research API Documentation\",\"description\":\"Gather and analyze the documentation for the new API to understand its endpoints, authentication methods, and data formats.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Create API Client\",\"description\":\"Develop a client library in C# (e.g., Services/NewApiClient.cs) that encapsulates the API's functionality and handles requests/responses.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify API Integration\",\"description\":\"Test the new API client by calling various endpoints to ensure it returns expected data and handles errors correctly.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T04:10:32", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 426. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
