 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Refactor legacy WPF applications to use modern .NET features."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Refactor legacy WPF applications to modern .NET features by researching new capabilities, updating MainWindow.xaml with modern controls, enhancing App.xaml for themes and styles, and thoroughly testing the refactored application\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research Modern .NET Features for WPF Applications\",\"description\":\"Explore new and upcoming features in .NET that can enhance the performance, security, and maintainability of legacy WPF applications. Identify specific features that are relevant to WPF development.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Refactor MainWindow.xaml\",\"description\":\"Refactor the MainWindow.xaml file by replacing outdated controls with modern alternatives provided by .NET, such as MahApps.Metro or Avalonia UI.\"},{\"role\":\"UIDEVELOPER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Update App.xaml for Theme and Styles\",\"description\":\"Update the App.xaml file to use modern theming and styling features. Ensure that the application adheres to the latest design guidelines and provides a consistent user experience.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify Refactoring\",\"description\":\"Perform thorough testing of the refactored application to ensure that all functionality is intact, performance has improved, and there are no regressions. Document any issues or bugs encountered during testing.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T04:14:28", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 431. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
