 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Implement a PowerShell script to automate data extraction from an SQL database and export to CSV."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Identify required modules, create connection script, verify database connection, then extract data and export to CSV using PowerShell\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Identify Required Modules\",\"description\":\"Research and identify any necessary PowerShell modules for connecting to an SQL database and exporting data to CSV.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Create Connection Script\",\"description\":\"Develop a PowerShell script file (e.g., ConnectToDatabase.ps1) that establishes a connection to the SQL database using the identified modules.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify Database Connection\",\"description\":\"Test the connection script to ensure it successfully connects to the SQL database.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Data Extraction and Export Script\",\"description\":\"Create a PowerShell script file (e.g., ExtractAndExport.ps1) that extracts data from the database using SQL queries and exports it to a CSV file.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T05:26:39", "notes