 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: 15. Implement rate limiting in our API to prevent abuse and ensure fair usage."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Conduct research on rate limiting strategies, implement the Token Bucket Algorithm in middleware, and integrate it into our API to enforce fair usage limits\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research Rate Limiting Strategies\",\"description\":\"Gather information on different rate limiting strategies, their pros and cons, and how they can be implemented in our API.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Implement Token Bucket Algorithm\",\"description\":\"Create a C# class for the Token Bucket algorithm in a new file named 'RateLimiting/TokenBucket.cs'. This should include methods to add tokens and check if requests can proceed.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Integrate Rate Limiting Middleware\",\"description\":\"Develop a middleware component in a new file named 'Middleware/RateLimitingMiddleware.cs' that uses the Token Bucket algorithm to limit API requests based on user or IP address.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify Rate Limiting Functionality\",\"description\":\"Test the rate limiting middleware by sending multiple requests from different IPs and users to ensure it correctly blocks excessive requests.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T05:28:21", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 581. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
