 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: 14. Develop a feature in our C#/WPF app that allows users to set reminders for upcoming events."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Design a reminder system using C# events, bind it to a WPF calendar view, implement data storage with Entity Framework, and test reminders through unit tests and user acceptance testing\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research Reminder Implementation Approaches\",\"description\":\"Identify and research various approaches to implementing reminder functionality in a C#/WPF application, considering factors such as database storage, event scheduling, and UI integration.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Design and Implement Reminder Data Model\",\"description\":\"Create the data model for reminders, including properties such as EventName, EventDate, User, and NotificationStatus. Define classes like Reminder.cs and ReminderService.cs in the Services folder.\"},{\"role\":\"UIDEVELOPER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Design and Implement Reminder UI\",\"description\":\"Design a user interface for setting reminders, including fields for entering event details and selecting notification preferences. Create XAML files such as ReminderWindow.xaml and ReminderForm.xaml in the Views folder.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify Reminder Functionality\",\"description\":\"Test the reminder feature to ensure that reminders are created, stored, and triggered correctly based on user input. Verify that notifications are sent as expected at the scheduled time.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T05:32:15", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 589. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
