 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: 29. Create a PowerShell script to automate the installation of software packages on multiple machines."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Identify suitable PowerShell modules, develop an automated script for package installation, test it thoroughly, and document its usage\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research existing PowerShell modules for package management\",\"description\":\"Identify and document any existing PowerShell modules or scripts that can be used for automating the installation of software packages on multiple machines.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Develop a PowerShell script for package installation\",\"description\":\"Create a PowerShell script named Install-Packages.ps1 that uses an appropriate module to install software packages on multiple target machines. The script should accept parameters for the list of machines and the packages to be installed.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Test the PowerShell script in a controlled environment\",\"description\":\"Verify that the Install-Packages.ps1 script functions correctly by testing it on a small set of target machines with known software installations. Ensure that the script can accurately install specified packages and handle errors gracefully.\"},{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Document the PowerShell script usage\",\"description\":\"Create documentation explaining how to use the Install-Packages.ps1 script, including parameter options, expected inputs, and potential outputs or error messages.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T05:32:42", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 591. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
