 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: 9. Refactor the authentication logic in our WPF application to use JWT tokens instead of cookies."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Refactor authentication to use JWT tokens by updating the service, modifying login/logout screens, and verifying the workflow\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research JWT Token Implementation\",\"description\":\"Explore and document JWT token implementation for WPF applications, focusing on libraries like System.IdentityModel.Tokens.Jwt.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Update Authentication Service\",\"description\":\"Refactor the AuthenticationService.cs to use JWT tokens instead of cookies for authentication processes.\"},{\"role\":\"UIDEVELOPER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Modify Login/Logout Screens\",\"description\":\"Revise the login and logout screens in MainWindow.xaml and MainWindow.xaml.cs to accommodate JWT token handling.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify Authentication Workflow\",\"description\":\"Test the entire authentication workflow to ensure that users can log in and out using JWT tokens, and that the application behaves as expected.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T05:34:23", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 594. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
