 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: 18. Refactor the data retrieval logic in our WPF app to use asynchronous programming."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Refactor UserService.cs and MainWindow.xaml.cs to implement async data retrieval using best practices identified during research\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research best practices for asynchronous data retrieval in WPF\",\"description\":\"Review existing literature, guidelines, and best practices for performing asynchronous operations in a WPF application.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Refactor UserService.cs to use async methods\",\"description\":\"Convert all synchronous calls within the UserService class to their asynchronous counterparts (e.g., Replace GetUsers() with GetUsersAsync()).\"},{\"role\":\"UIDEVELOPER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Update MainWindow.xaml.cs to handle async data retrieval\",\"description\":\"Modify the event handlers in MainWindow.xaml.cs to call the asynchronous methods from UserService and update the UI accordingly.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify asynchronous data retrieval functionality\",\"description\":\"Test that the application retrieves data asynchronously without blocking the UI, and that the UI updates correctly when data is received.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T05:34:33", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 595. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
