 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: 53. Create a PowerShell script to automate the generation of invoices from purchase data."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Develop a PowerShell script by researching relevant cmdlets, reading purchase data, generating invoices, and testing the script\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research PowerShell cmdlets for file manipulation and data processing\",\"description\":\"Identify and document PowerShell cmdlets that will be used for reading, manipulating, and exporting invoice data.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Develop script to read purchase data\",\"description\":\"Create a PowerShell script named 'ReadPurchaseData.ps1' that reads purchase data from a CSV file and stores it in an array of objects.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Develop script to generate invoices\",\"description\":\"Create a PowerShell script named 'GenerateInvoices.ps1' that processes the purchase data to calculate invoice totals and formats them into an invoice structure.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Test the PowerShell scripts\",\"description\":\"Execute both scripts with sample data to ensure they read the data correctly, calculate invoices accurately, and format the output as expected.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T05:35:06", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 596. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
