 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Integrate a REST API into a WPF application for fetching user information."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Design and implement a WPF application with an API service class to fetch user information using REST endpoints, followed by data model creation and integration verification\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research REST API Endpoints\",\"description\":\"Identify the endpoints and required parameters for fetching user information from the backend service.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Create API Service Class\",\"description\":\"Develop a new class in Services folder (e.g., UserService.cs) to handle HTTP requests to the REST API.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Implement Data Model for User\",\"description\":\"Create a data model class in Models folder (e.g., User.cs) that represents the structure of user information returned by the API.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify API Integration\",\"description\":\"Test the API service methods to ensure they correctly fetch and parse user information from the backend.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T05:56:11", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_o