 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Create a PowerShell function that checks disk space on multiple servers and alerts via email if any drive is below 10% free space."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Write a PowerShell function to check disk space on multiple servers, validate its functionality, and configure email settings for alerts\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Write PowerShell Script\",\"description\":\"Create a PowerShell script named 'CheckDiskSpace.ps1' that connects to multiple servers and checks the free space on each drive. The script should alert via email if any drive is below 10% free space.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Validate Script Functionality\",\"description\":\"Run the 'CheckDiskSpace.ps1' script against a test environment with simulated server data and verify that it correctly identifies drives with less than 10% free space and sends an email alert.\"},{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Configure Email Settings\",\"description\":\"Research how to configure PowerShell to send emails from the script. Ensure that the script uses a valid SMTP server and appropriate credentials if necessary.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T06:04:31", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 649. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
