 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Optimize the WPF app's performance by reducing CPU usage during heavy operations"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Analyze CPU usage, optimize heavy operations, implement background processing, and validate performance improvements\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Analyze CPU Usage\",\"description\":\"Use profiling tools to identify which parts of the application are consuming the most CPU resources during heavy operations.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Optimize Heavy Operations\",\"description\":\"Refactor the code in Services/HeavyOperationService.cs and WorkerThreads/HeavyWorkerThread.cs to reduce CPU usage. Consider parallel processing, lazy loading, or more efficient algorithms where applicable.\"},{\"role\":\"UIDEVELOPER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Implement Background Processing\",\"description\":\"Refactor the UI in MainWindow.xaml.cs to use asynchronous programming (async/await) for heavy operations, ensuring the UI remains responsive. Use Task.Run() for background threads and Dispatcher.Invoke() when updating UI elements from background tasks.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Validate Performance Improvements\",\"description\":\"Run performance tests to ensure that CPU usage during heavy operations has been reduced. Compare the results before and after optimization.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T06:12:55", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 690. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
