 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Refactor the data processing pipeline to handle large datasets efficiently."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Refactor the data processing pipeline by analyzing its current state, implementing batch processing to handle large datasets efficiently, optimizing data storage for faster access, and validating batch processing functionality through rigorous testing\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Analyze current data processing pipeline\",\"description\":\"Review existing codebase and identify bottlenecks, memory usage, and performance issues.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Implement batch processing\",\"description\":\"Refactor the pipeline to process data in batches rather than all at once. Update relevant files such as DataProcessor.cs.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Optimize data storage\",\"description\":\"Refactor database queries and usage to improve performance and reduce memory footprint. Update StorageService.cs.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Validate batch processing functionality\",\"description\":\"Ensure that the new batch processing system handles large datasets without errors and performs within acceptable time limits.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_mo