 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Refactor an existing PowerShell script to improve readability and maintainability by breaking it into smaller functions."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Refactor PowerShell script by researching current code, creating new functions, testing separation, and verifying refactoring\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Understand Current Script\",\"description\":\"Review the existing PowerShell script to identify logical sections that can be refactored into separate functions.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Create New Functions\",\"description\":\"For each identified section, create a new function in a new file named 'RefactoredScript.ps1'. Each function should have a clear, descriptive name and a single responsibility.\"},{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Test Function Separation\",\"description\":\"Ensure that each function works as expected when called independently. Note any dependencies or shared state that needs to be managed between functions.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify Refactored Script\",\"description\":\"Run the refactored script and verify that it produces the same output as the original script while being more readable and maintainable.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-12T23:57:18", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 789. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
