 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Develop an API client library in C# for a third-party service, making it easier to integrate their services into other applications."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Gather documentation, create a base class, implement endpoints, and test integration\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Gather Third-Party Service Documentation\",\"description\":\"Research and gather all necessary documentation for the third-party service API, including endpoints, authentication methods, request/response formats, and any specific requirements or limitations.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Create API Client Base Class\",\"description\":\"Develop a base class in C# (e.g., ThirdPartyClient.cs) that handles common functionalities such as authentication, error handling, and request/response serialization/deserialization.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Implement Specific API Endpoints\",\"description\":\"Create classes for specific API endpoints (e.g., UsersApi.cs, OrdersApi.cs), implementing methods to interact with the third-party service according to their documentation.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify Integration\",\"description\":\"Test the API client library by integrating it into a sample application or using automated tests to ensure that all endpoints are working correctly and that data is being exchanged as expected.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-12T23:57:54", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 790. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
