 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Implement caching mechanisms in a C# WPF application to improve performance by reducing network calls."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Implement MemoryCache in the WPF application's data service to cache data, reducing network calls and improving performance\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research Caching Strategies\",\"description\":\"Explore different caching strategies and libraries suitable for a C# WPF application, such as MemoryCache or third-party libraries like Redis or Azure Cache.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Implement MemoryCache\",\"description\":\"Create a singleton class (e.g., CacheService.cs) that uses System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache to store and retrieve data temporarily.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Integrate Caching in Data Service\",\"description\":\"Modify the data service layer (e.g., DataService.cs) to check cache before making network calls. If data is available in cache, return it; otherwise, fetch from the network and store in cache.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify Caching Implementation\",\"description\":\"Test various scenarios to ensure that caching reduces network calls effectively and handles edge cases like cache expiration or invalidation.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-12T23:58:20", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 792. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
