 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Integrate a REST API in a WPF application to fetch and display user data in real-time."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Integrate a REST API in a WPF application by creating a service class for API requests, designing a UI to display user data, and verifying functionality through testing\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research available libraries for REST API integration\",\"description\":\"Explore and document existing libraries that can be used to integrate a REST API into a WPF application.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Create a service class to handle API requests\",\"description\":\"Develop a C# class (e.g., Services/UserService.cs) that uses the chosen library to make GET requests to fetch user data.\"},{\"role\":\"UIDEVELOPER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Design the UI to display user data\",\"description\":\"Create XAML and code-behind files (e.g., Views/UserView.xaml, Views/UserView.xaml.cs) to design a layout that displays user data in real-time.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify API integration and UI functionality\",\"description\":\"Test the application to ensure that the REST API is successfully fetching data and that the UI accurately displays it in real-time.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-12T23:59:00", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 794. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
