 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Integrate a REST API in a WPF application to fetch and display user data in real-time."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Integrate REST API in WPF app using async/await for real-time user data fetching, display with MVVM pattern\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research existing REST APIs for user data fetching\",\"description\":\"Identify suitable REST APIs that provide user data and understand their endpoints, authentication methods, and response formats.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Create a UserService to handle API requests\",\"description\":\"Implement the UserService.cs class in the Services folder. This class should include methods for fetching user data from the REST API using HttpClient.\"},{\"role\":\"UIDEVELOPER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Design and implement the User Interface\",\"description\":\"Create a new UserControl named UserDisplay.xaml in the UI/Controls folder. Design the layout to display user data, including properties such as name, email, and profile picture.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify API integration and UI functionality\",\"description\":\"Test the UserService methods for fetching user data from the REST API. Ensure that the UserDisplay control correctly displays user data in real-time when new data is received.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T00:00:03", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 795. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
