 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Develop an API client library in C# for a third-party service, making it easier to integrate their services into other applications."}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Conduct research on the third-party service's API, design and implement a C# client library, and thoroughly test its integration capabilities\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research Third-Party Service API\",\"description\":\"Gather documentation and examples of the third-party service's API.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Create API Client Library\",\"description\":\"Develop a C# library (e.g., ThirdPartyApiClient.cs) that encapsulates the API endpoints and provides methods for common operations.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify API Integration\",\"description\":\"Test the client library by integrating it into a sample application to ensure it functions correctly with the third-party service.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-13T00:00:09", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 796. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
