 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Implement a CSV export feature for the data grid that handles Unicode filenames"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Implement a CSV export feature using a Unicode-aware library, integrate it into the data grid, and validate its functionality\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research on CSV Exporting Libraries\",\"description\":\"Investigate and identify suitable libraries for handling CSV exporting in .NET, focusing on support for Unicode characters and filename validation.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Implement CSV Export Logic\",\"description\":\"Create a service class named Services/ExportService.cs that includes methods for exporting data grid content to CSV format. Ensure the implementation supports Unicode characters in both data and filenames.\"},{\"role\":\"UIDEVELOPER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Integrate CSV Export Feature into Data Grid\",\"description\":\"Update the UI component responsible for displaying the data grid to include a button or option for exporting data. Ensure that this feature correctly invokes the export logic from Services/ExportService.cs.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Validate CSV Export Functionality\",\"description\":\"Test the CSV export feature with various datasets containing Unicode characters and filenames to ensure correct handling and no errors.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-12T21:34:43", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 852. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
