 no preamble, no trailing text.\nString values MUST NOT contain literal newlines — use \\n inside strings if needed.\n{\n  \"plan\": \"one-sentence overall approach\",\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"RESEARCHER\",\n      \"priority\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"Short descriptive title\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed, self-contained instructions for this minion. Use \\n for line breaks inside this string.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}, {"role": "user", "content": "Goal: Add a system tray icon that shows notification count and allows quick navigation"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": "{\"plan\":\"Develop a SystemTrayIconService in C# to integrate a notification count icon with quick navigation options, incorporating research, design, and testing phases\",\"tasks\":[{\"role\":\"RESEARCHER\",\"priority\":1,\"title\":\"Research system tray icons in C#\",\"description\":\"Investigate existing libraries and frameworks for creating system tray icons in C#. Identify any potential libraries that provide the necessary functionality, including displaying a notification count and quick navigation options.\"},{\"role\":\"CODER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Create SystemTrayIconService.cs\",\"description\":\"Develop a service class named `SystemTrayIconService.cs` that handles the creation and management of the system tray icon. This class should include methods to update the notification count, handle clicks, and manage the quick navigation options.\"},{\"role\":\"UIDEVELOPER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Design System Tray Icon Menu\",\"description\":\"Design a context menu for the system tray icon that includes options for quick navigation. Create an XAML file named `SystemTrayMenu.xaml` to define the layout of the menu.\"},{\"role\":\"TESTER\",\"priority\":2,\"title\":\"Verify System Tray Icon Functionality\",\"description\":\"Test the system tray icon functionality to ensure that the notification count updates correctly, and that the quick navigation options are functional. Verify that clicking on the system tray icon opens the application window.\"}]}"}], "metadata": {"category": "boss_planning", "task_type": "feature_plan", "source": "hardcorepc_normalized", "quality": "silver", "contains_sensitive_data": false, "base_model_target": "theorc-boss:gemma4", "created_by": "normalize_hardcorepc_boss.py", "original_model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b", "original_generated": "2026-06-12T21:39:24", "notes": "Normalized from hardcorepc_raw_overnight.jsonl example 860. Plan generated by qwen2.5-coder:7b."}}
